---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="New here? — Matej Vavro">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 max-w-4xl">
		<main class="space-y-12">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8">New here?</h1>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Obsidian Intro</h2>
				<div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333333] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8">
					<p class="text-lg text-[#e5e5e5] leading-relaxed mb-4">
						Obsidian is a powerful knowledge base that works on top of a local folder of plain text Markdown files. It's the foundation of my Second Brain system and the platform where all my productivity plugins live.
					</p>
					<p class="text-lg text-[#e5e5e5] leading-relaxed">
						If you're new to Obsidian, start by understanding how it can transform your note-taking and knowledge management. It's not just a tool—it's a system for thinking, organizing, and building clarity.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Best Videos</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-[#a0a0a0] mb-6">
					Start with these essential videos to understand my approach to productivity and Second Brain systems:
				</p>
				<ul class="space-y-4 mb-6">
					<li class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333333] rounded-lg p-6">
						<a
							href="https://www.youtube.com/@MatejVavroProductivity"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer"
							class="text-[#ff0000] hover:text-[#ff3333] font-semibold text-lg transition-colors"
						>
							Getting Started with Obsidian
						</a>
						<p class="text-sm text-[#a0a0a0] mt-2">Learn the fundamentals of building your Second Brain</p>
					</li>
					<li class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333333] rounded-lg p-6">
						<a
							href="https://www.youtube.com/@MatejVavroProductivity"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer"
							class="text-[#ff0000] hover:text-[#ff3333] font-semibold text-lg transition-colors"
						>
							Plugin Overview & Workflow
						</a>
						<p class="text-sm text-[#a0a0a0] mt-2">See how my plugins work together</p>
					</li>
					<li class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333333] rounded-lg p-6">
						<a
							href="https://www.youtube.com/@MatejVavroProductivity"
							target="_blank"
							rel="noopener noreferrer"
							class="text-[#ff0000] hover:text-[#ff3333] font-semibold text-lg transition-colors"
						>
							Advanced Productivity Systems
						</a>
						<p class="text-sm text-[#a0a0a0] mt-2">Deep dive into automation and efficiency</p>
					</li>
				</ul>
				<p class="mt-6">
					<a
						href="https://www.youtube.com/@MatejVavroProductivity"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						class="text-[#ff0000] hover:text-[#ff3333] font-semibold transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2"
					>
						View all videos on YouTube
						<svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
						</svg>
					</a>
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">Plugin Overview</h2>
				<p class="text-lg text-[#a0a0a0] mb-6">
					My Obsidian plugins are designed to work together as an ecosystem for productivity and knowledge management:
				</p>
				<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-1">
					<div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border-l-4 border-white rounded-lg p-6">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Prisma Calendar</h3>
						<p class="text-[#a0a0a0] mb-4">Advanced calendar system for Obsidian with powerful scheduling and planning capabilities.</p>
						<a href="/tools" class="text-white hover:text-[#a0a0a0] font-semibold transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2">
							Learn more
							<svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
							</svg>
						</a>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border-l-4 border-white rounded-lg p-6">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Periodix Planner</h3>
						<p class="text-[#a0a0a0] mb-4">Periodic planning and goal tracking system that helps you maintain focus and direction.</p>
						<a href="/tools" class="text-white hover:text-[#a0a0a0] font-semibold transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2">
							Learn more
							<svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
							</svg>
						</a>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border-l-4 border-white rounded-lg p-6">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Nexus Properties</h3>
						<p class="text-[#a0a0a0] mb-4">Property management system for organizing and connecting your knowledge base.</p>
						<a href="/tools" class="text-white hover:text-[#a0a0a0] font-semibold transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2">
							Learn more
							<svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
								<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
							</svg>
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="mt-6">
					<a
						href="/tools"
						class="text-white hover:text-[#a0a0a0] font-semibold transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2"
					>
						Explore all tools
						<svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
						</svg>
					</a>
				</p>
			</section>

			<div class="bg-[#1a1a1a] border border-[#333333] rounded-xl p-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Stay Updated</h3>
				<!-- Kit embed will go here -->
				<div class="min-h-[100px] flex items-center justify-center text-[#666] my-4 border border-dashed border-[#333333] rounded-lg">
					[Kit Newsletter Form Embed]
				</div>
				<p class="text-sm text-[#a0a0a0] italic text-center">
					No spam. I'll email only when there's something worth your time.
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
